caller_intent: German from Interbiomes wants to report a truck accident involving a deer and initiate a claim with Ancients, seeking guidance on the process.
resolution_steps: Cody confirms the accident details (deer collision damaging a truck used by Ancients).
Cody instructs German to send photos and a detailed description of the incident (time, location, extent of damage).
Cody assures German that the claim will be filed once the information is received.
knowledge_required: Insurance claims process for vehicle damage
summary: German reports a truck damaged in a deer collision and seeks to file a claim with Ancients. Cody guides him to provide photos and incident details for processing. The call concludes with German agreeing to send the required information.
